org.sql: SELECT time_entries.* FROM time_entries INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = time_entries.project_id WHERE time_entries.created_on BETWEEN '2022-02-04' AND '2022-02-14' AND time_entries.user_id = 2 AND projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'time_tracking') IS NOT NULL
